title: Wall Street Breakfast July 12: Euro Hits Parity with Dollar for First Time in Decades
author: Seeking Alpha

description: Euro hits parity with dollar for first time in decades. Twitter's lawyers step up, telling Musk his deal isn't ended. U.K. lawmakers pass windfall tax on oil and gas producers. Catch today’s WSB article here.
